This is release 0.8 of Galera - Codership's implementation of wsrep interface
(https://launchpad.net/wsrep/).

For details, see https://launchpad.net/galera/

Software Requirements:
* Scons build system (http://www.scons.org/)
* Check unit test library (http://check.sourceforge.net/)


To build Galera library just run 'scons' in the root directory.
Result of build will be 'libgalera_smm.so' library in the root directory.
This library is ready to use as a provider for wsrep-enabled app (MySQL).

For more information, see:
* Codership home page http://www.codership.com
* Codership mailing list http://groups.google.com/group/codership-team

